query error DataFusion error: This feature is not implemented: Unsupported ast node in sqltorel: Lambda\(LambdaFunction \{ params: One\(LambdaFunctionParameter \{ name: Ident \{ value: "v", quote_style: None, span: Span\(Location\(1,8\)\.\.Location\(1,9\)\) \}, data_type: None \}\), body: Identifier\(Ident \{ value: "v", quote_style: None, span: Span\(Location\(1,13\)\.\.Location\(1,14\)\) \}\), syntax: Arrow \}\)
