query error DataFusion error: This feature is not implemented: Unsupported ast node in sqltorel: Lambda\(LambdaFunction \{ params: One\(LambdaFunctionParameter \{ name: Ident \{ value: "v", quote_style: None, span: Span\(Location\(1,34\)\.\.Location\(1,35\)\) \}, data_type: None \}\), body: BinaryOp \{ left: Identifier\(Ident \{ value: "v", quote_style: None, span: Span\(Location\(1,39\)\.\.Location\(1,40\)\) \}\), op: Plus, right: Value\(ValueWithSpan \{ value: Number\("1", false\), span: Span\(Location\(1,41\)\.\.Location\(1,42\)\) \}\) \}, syntax: Arrow \}\)
